title: St. Michael-Albertville edges Monticello 27-26 in OT
text: St. Michael-Albertville edges Monticello 27-26 in overtime 10/08/2015, 9:45pm CDT By Jim Paulsen, Star Tribune Both teams scored touchdowns in the extra session, with the Knights converting their extra point try for the win. St. Michael-Albertville's Isaiah Weston looked to break into the open field in the first half. Weston caught two touchdown passes, including what proved to be the game-winner in overtime. Photo: Richard Tsong-Taatarii * rtsong-taatarii@startribune.com
